name: Krang
description:
Do you love relaxing in the sand, long days in the sun, and visceral terror that pierces your soul and devours your sanity from across the godforsaken desert of Mars? Krang does!

Collect all 1!

No souls were consumed in the creation of this image. Or they were, I don't know anything about it and I blame CLIP. Lovingly upscaled from 512x512 to 2048x2048.
